creator: CryptoSwapp.com
descriptionHtml:
CryptoSwapp: we're building the best p2p exchange service and here's what we focused on:


- Smooth chat system similar to what you're got used to: WhatsApp, Viber or Telegram.

- Push notifications of different kind, so you never miss a trade or new message.

- Ability to connect your Localbitcoins or Localethereum accounts, so you don't build your trading profile from the ground.

- Clean trade escrow workflow, understandable for newbies.

- Easiness to open a trade or post your own offer.

- Multiple cryptocurrency support, so you don't have to switch between services.

- Support which is always ready to listen for your complaints and feedback. Just write to us at support@cryptoswapp.com
